messages.message: :heads-up: our next <#C03UK2BB17X|> (10/7) is approaching and it will be another 4 day weekend for folks in :us: and :flag-ca: since 10/10 is a holiday. Here is a friendly heads up that our next major release 22.10 code cut will happen right after that weekend on 10/11. In case you plan to take additional days off, please start to work with your team to make sure features and UAT will be covered. :pray:
